ve/perm/wiki operation.\n\nActually, wait - I need to re-read my instructions more carefully. The task says:\n- \"向主 session 汇报结果（用 sessions_send）\" - but I don't have this tool\n- Messages should be returned as plain text for the main agent to deliver\n\nActually, looking at the general subagent instructions: \"Only use the `message` tool when explicitly instructed to contact a specific external recipient; otherwise return plain text and let the main agent deliver it\"\n\nAnd the task says to notify in the Feishu group and report to the main session. Since I can't directly send Feishu messages (no such tool available), I should:\n1. Return the results as plain text\n2. The main agent will handle the Feishu notification\n\nLet me clean up the temp script first, then provide my final report.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Y3J5aPbYJFQC31OAlWBn1907","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"del \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\check_hotupdate.ps1\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3637,"output":752,"cacheRead":21504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25893,"cost":{"input":0.00050918,"output":0.00021056000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000602112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001321852}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778829596561,"responseId":"fd6059ba-4f4e-4fbf-a466-ef2f4b944bd1"}}
