{"type":"message","id":"01456bb6","parentId":"1615c569","timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:20:16.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, the pipeline has completed. Let me summarize the results for the main session.\n\nLet me also check the performance summary - BuildAssetBundles took about 1026 seconds (17 minutes), but total pipeline execution seems much shorter because the CDN upload step immediately fell through to local test mode. Let me look at the timestamps:\n- \"begin 'Excute Pipline:上传CDN'\" at 12:40:32\n- \"end 'Excute Pipline:上传CDN'\" at 12:40:33 (only 1 second - because it failed and went to local test mode)\n\nAnd the overall pipeline started earlier. The build took about 1000+ seconds for asset bundles. Let me check the performance summary more carefully.\n\nActually, the performance data shows:\n- BuildAssetBundles: 3 samples, Peak 952s, Total 1026s\n\nSo the total build time was about 17 minutes for asset bundles.\n\nNow let me provide my final report.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ 热更流水线执行完成\n\n### 结果汇总\n\n| 步骤 | 状态 | 详情 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 构建检查 | ✅ | 无正在执行的热更流水线 |\n| Unity 引擎启动 | ✅ | 许可证验证通过 |\n| Asset Bundle 构建 | ✅ | 耗时约 17 分钟，BuildAssetBundles 完成，Build Successful ×2 |\n| Bundle 加密 | ✅ | 文件加密完成 |\n| CDN 上传 | ⚠️ | 进入**本地测试模式**（CDN git 仓库未配置，无法上传，但本地测试环境已就绪） |\n| 本地测试环境 | ✅ | 已准备就绪：`D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.44` |\n\n### 流水线输出\n- 版本号：**1.0.44**\n- 渠道：**Test1** (Android/StandaloneWindows64)\n- 本地测试目录：`D:/cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.44`\n\n### CDN 上传失败原因\n1. `fatal: not a git repository` — CDN git 仓库未在本地配置\n2. `(404) Not Found` — 下载 CDN 文件时返回 404\n\n但流水线以降级模式继续执行，设置了本地测试环境。\n\n### 需要主 session 处理\n在飞书群 **月圆之夜CCG开发群** 中 @兵王(周以天) 通知更新完成：\n> `<at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>` 测试服已更新到 v1.0.44，Asset Bundle 构建完成。CDN 上传步骤因本地 git 仓库未配置而降级为本地测试模式。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepsee